snippet: Manuel Torres scored twice to lead Panama in the first round of the Concacaf Gold Cup at the Rose Bowl, stunning the pro-Mexico crowd.
abstract: Panama defeats Mexico, 2-1, in first round of soccer's Concacaf Gold Cup at the Rose Bowl in Pasadena, Calif.
lead_paragraph: Manuel Torres scored twice to lead Panama in the first round of the Concacaf Gold Cup at the Rose Bowl, stunning the pro-Mexico crowd.

headline.main: Panama Defeats Mexico in Concacaf Gold Cup
